a.title:
v2 release prep (#733)
* wip
* move files around to their new location
- `solid` -> `24/solid` - `mini` -> `20/solid` - `outilne` -> `24/outline`
* rename svgo configs to reflect new names
The diff is a little bit confusing. It looks like it moved `svgo.filled.yaml` to `svgo.20.solid.yaml` but that should have been `mini`.
The reason it does this is simply becaue the contents of `svgo.filled.yaml` and `svgo.mini.yaml` are the same.
* rename optimized files
* update paths in build scripts
* ensure to publish the files in the 20,24 folders
* update README documentation
* update README logo's
* change dimensions of logo a bit
Co-authored-by: Brad Cornes <hello@bradley.dev>
